title: Monica Toy
description:
Welcome to the official channel of Monica Toy. If you’re looking for videos of Monica, Jimmy Five, Maggy, Smudge and Milena; of the escapades of Chuck Billy ‘N’ Folks; and of endless other characters from the Mauricio de Sousa universe, you’ve come to the right place. Plus, we’ll give you the inside scoop on cartoon production, take you backstage to some of our shows and so much more.
